<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .header { color:rgb(51, 72, 92); }
      .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color:rgb(132, 149, 150); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 class="header">Hi <%= @student.first_name %>,</h1>
    
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that the course "<strong><%= @course.title %></strong>" is ending in 3 days.</p>
    
    <p>Course end date: <strong><%= @course.ends_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong></p>
    
    <p>Make sure to complete all your assignments and review the course materials before it ends!</p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact your instructor.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Studidi Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>